# Job freshness

- Catalog queries must filter `status = active` AND (`expiresAt IS NULL OR expiresAt > now()`).
- Provider sync sets `lastCheckedAt` on every check; `markStaleByProvider` closes missing jobs.
- Never recommend or list `closed` / `expired` jobs in search, dashboard top jobs, or match results.
